Package com.cyberfront.crdt.sample.data

Class AbstractDataType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyberfront.crdt.sample.data.AbstractDataType
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimpleBoolean, SimpleCollection, SimpleDouble, SimpleInteger, SimpleReference, SimpleString
    public abstract class AbstractDataType
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the abstract base class for the test data elements which are coded as JSON objects in the CRDT elements under test
